name: Omkar Engineering
overview:
Established in the year, 1980, we, “Omkar Engineering Works”, are an established entity of the market engaged in manufacturing and exporting a finest quality array of Sulzer Projectile Weaving Machine Spare Parts to our deemed patrons. Products that we offer encompass Picking Mechanism, Projectile Feeder Drive, Picking Lock, Projectile Feeder, Projectile Lifter, Projectile Opener, Conveyor Drive and Sulzer Weaving Unit.

Our Team: Experienced engineers Technicians Quality controllers Marketing agents

Our Quality Assurance: With the prime objective of providing the best, we are engaged in offering Sulzer Projectile Weaving Machine Spare Parts. To fulfill our objectives, we precisely develop all our products using supreme quality material, procured from the established vendors of the markets.

Our Infrastructure: Designing unit Quality testing unit Warehouse Administration office

Client Satisfaction: We are a well driven name of the industry engaged in putting our best foot forward to offer an excellent range of Picking Mechanism, Projectile Feeder Drive, Picking Lock, Projectile Feeder, Projectile Lifter, Projectile Opener and many more in order to create cordial relationship with the patrons.
